data.description: A home for the holidays! This 1-bed, 1.5-bath condo boasts a spacious layout, a private patio, and modern upgrades like kitchen recessed lighting and a new Samsung refrigerator. Recently remodeled bathrooms feature upgraded vanities and fixtures. Enjoy separate dining and living areas, an open kitchen, and a roomy bedroom with a large walk-in closet. Conveniently located near shops, restaurants, and entertainment, with easy access to the Turnpike and major highways. Security is ensured with a keyed lobby entrance, and on-site laundry adds to the convenience. The community, suitable for all ages, offers amenities like a gym, pool, and tennis courts. All offers will be reviewed on Tuesday, 11/28/23. Make this charming condo your home for the holidays!
